metadata.name: Thoughts and feelings in voices
metadata.description:
Self-confidence, enchantment, dignity. Attractive involving emotions, when it's not aloowed to get close, but one is lured with charisma, accompanied with modest extraversion. Yet behind the mask of broadcasted indifference and impertinence, one may sense the warmth comes from the depths.

100x50 cm.* Acrylic on canvas.
Author Pictor.O.M.
2021

* In the initial sale from the author, the physical original of the work is attached to the lot. Shipping is included in the price and is available via DHL only. (only to those places where delivery by dhl service is possible)
